OL,5, Six police constables have lost their  
OL,6, jobs for being part of a WhatsApp group
OL,7, sharing "grossly offensive" messages.  
OL,9,FMore than 6,000 messages were viewed by
OL,10,Fthe Independent Office for Police      
OL,11,FConduct (IOPC), including racist and   
OL,12,Fhomophobic comments, derogatory remarks
OL,13,Fabout domestic abuse victims, people   
OL,14,Fwith disabilities, and women.          
OL,16,FThe officers from three forces were    
OL,17,Ffound to be guilty of gross misconduct.
OL,19,FTwo were sacked and the others would   
OL,20,Fhave been if they had not already left.
